(227, 5, 'When Fire Breaks Out', 'Regardless of the size of the fire, ALWAYS contact the fire department. Never assume that someone else has called. Then contact the Team Leader to apprise him/her of the situation.\nTeam Leader determines if emergency plan activation is necessary.\nI plan is activated, ALL operations shut down to deal with the fire.\nResponse Team goes into action.\nAssist emergency fire and police personnel and other emergency management personnelk when asked.', 1, '2011-10-12 18:02:44', 1),
