(36, 'Each floor captain check all units are empty and direct tenants to nearest stairwell. Once outside of building all tenants and staff gather outside 192 E Indiana Ave and report to head duty monitor.', 'Floors 3-6 to front of building exit by stairs to courtyard. Floors 3-6 to rear of building exit by stairs to street. Floors LL-2 to front of building exit by stairs to Main entrance. Floors LL-2 to rear of building exit by stairs to street. *Tenants on lower level use exit to courtyard if necessary.*', 'na', 39, 195, '2013-11-12 01:53:13', '2013-11-12 01:53:13', 1),
(37, 'Sound the building alarm\r\nCheck elevators and shut down if necessary\r\nStart on the 4th floor and work down to assist the elderly and disabled to evacuate\r\nCheck non-residential areas: fitness center, storage areas, clubroom, upper garage, lower garage, basement trash room', 'Bldg A (west end): Exit west stairs at 1st floor & assemble at large gate.  Units 101-108, 201-208, 301-308, 401-408\r\nBldg A (east end): Exit east stairs at 1st floor & assemble at tennis gate. Units 109-114, 209-216, 309-316, 409-416\r\nBldg B (north end): Exit north stairs at basement & assemble at pool gate. Units B1, 126-134, 2290237, 329-337, 429-437\r\nBldg B (south end): Exit south stairs at 1st floor & assemble at sidewalk gate. Units 217-228, 317-328, 417-428\r\nBldg B (1st floor only) Exit main entrance at 1st floor & assemble at visitor parking. Units 115-125\r\nBldg B (ground floor only): Exit west entrance at ground level & assemble at pool gate. Units 001-014', 'If a stairwell is inacessible, redirect the evacuation to the closet passable stairwells & hallways\r\nUse the closet accessible balcony as necessary\r\nDirect residents without balaconies to the closest accessible nearby apartment''s balcony for evacuation', 37, 201, '2013-11-13 22:59:46', '2013-11-13 22:59:46', 1),
(38, 'Building EVACUATION: Maintenance Staff and Emergency personnel in all building stairwells with ample portable lighting\r\nBeBe will check Building #2        Jack will check Building #1        Paul will check Building # 3        Rodney will check Building #4\r\nThe procedure will be to knock on each door and open each door to ensure all persons have evacuated\r\nIn the event you cannot access a unit contact the EMERGENCY Personel on site and have them open door (this is last resort) \r\nIf time permits have someone go to shop and get keys', 'Have all residents EXIT through stairs.  Absolutely NO ONE to exit thru ELEVATORS\r\nHave all residents gather at established RESIDENT COMMAND CENTER', 'If a stairwell is inaccessible, redirect the evacuation to the closest passable stairwells and hallways. Use the closest accessible balcony as necessary. Direct residents without balconies to the closest accessible nearby apartment''s balcony for evacuation. ', 37, 21, '2013-11-14 00:50:02', '2014-05-05 19:08:25', 1),
