(45, 'This will depend on the nature and degree of the disaster.\r\nAll residents and employees must exit the building using the closet door to their location.\r\nAll persons should be directed to move as far away from the disaster as possible.', 'Based on Building Location\r\nGroup A   Buildings - A,B,C,D,E,F,G,H,J      Leave from main exit that goes to Maple Ave\r\nGroup B  Buildings - V,S,T,W,Y,P,M,N,R,Q,X,O    Leave from Stratford Drive\r\nGroup C  Buildings - K,L,AB,AA,Z,AE,AD,AC,AF,AG,AH,AJ,AK   Leave from School Road', 'TBD', 37, 24, '2013-11-18 20:09:08', '2013-11-18 20:09:08', 1),
